      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">6</infon>
        <offset>887</offset>
        <text>Here we evaluate how aridity affects the balance between C, N and P in soils collected from 224 dryland sites from all continents except Antarctica.
</text>
        <annotation id="T14">
          <infon key="brat-id">T14</infon>
